name: HL7 Version 2 Model Elements
title: HL7 Version 2 Model Elements
description:
This code system defines HL7 Version 2 Model Elements used for Version 2 to FHIR Translation
This subset addresses model elements used for conversion of V2-FHIR Mapping - Data Type: CNN
Source data can be found at https://confluence.hl7.org/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=40730805
